    "gp_section_575381853616341535": {
      "settings": {
        "checksum": "d69e8a89720b3a908dbef3440e288be83acd86d77ff157f4e991488b6c5fe047_1_1_1_0__1",
        "gg-E0zj8IYQ_text": "<p>Even expensive mattresses or gadgets miss the mark. If your hips and spine aren't kept in proper alignment, the damage continues.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Finally, a lot of people try to fix this misalignment lock by placing a regular pillow between their knees. But those pillows usually slip, flatten, or just don’t provide enough support. And every night, their spine falls back out of alignment, leading to that exruciating pain.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>However, if you thought of a pillow between your legs too, you’re on the right track! You definitely need to keep your hips and spine aligned while you sleep. But if a regular pillow isn’t the right solution, then what is?</p>",
        "gg00qBxiwoT_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-b39bd931-c2c0-476d-8578-3c2e153fd0d6.jpg",
        "gg16emhghS4_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-5177da4b-16e3-42fd-aa02-408bebb2c072.jpg",
        "gg16emhghS4_srcSet_mobile_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-59d65c5d-2422-44bf-9deb-ddd38083c961.jpg",
        "gg1gxB-NXpY_text": "<p>\"I originally bought the SmoothSpine™ Alignment Pillow for my daughter who works long hours at a computer and <strong>constantly complains of hip pain.</strong> After seeing how much it helped her, I ordered one for myself too. We both feel a noticeable difference after using it for just a few minutes each night. <strong>It’s easy to use, comfortable, and works like a charm.</strong>\"</p>",
        "gg2Hufy-Ooh_text": "<p>\"I bought the SmoothSpine™ Alignment Pillow for myself and one for my husband. We both use it every evening to relax before bed. <strong>It gently aligns our hips and relieves so much of the day’s tension.</strong> We’ve both been sleeping better and waking up without the usual stiffness. It’s honestly one of the <strong>best wellness purchases</strong> we’ve made in years.\"</p>",
        "gg4UiviMG9p_text": "Alignment Pillow",
        "gg5Uia2v6fi_text": "<p>Even surgery consultations</p>",
        "gg6sZSk6gMV_text": "<p>I slept through the night without waking up from pain for the first time in years! I had no pain in the morning as well. Although, I still felt some stiffness in my lower back.</p>",
        "gg912yBeZeE_text": "Why Most Solutions Don’t Work",
        "ggAkz1jQVJC_text": "Rated 4.8/5 | 10,674+ Customers",
        "ggApD-e2CTH_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-b6c4c810-edd0-48eb-86d1-73a91578b8bd.jpg",
        "ggBTtYTKPEP_text": "<p>This isn’t just about Laura. Over 57,000 people now use the SmoothSpine Alignment Pillow. Most feel relief within days.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>And it’s 100% risk-free: there’s a 90-night guarantee. Use it. Try it. If you don’t feel real results, return it. No questions.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>But please — use it consistently. One night won’t undo years of damage.</strong></p>",
        "ggCrFeXtw36_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-cb5f87ef-bbf9-40fa-a100-141946a4fb73.png",
        "ggCrJm6zHQy_label": "<p>Night 1:</p>",
        "ggE6IO9oUh8_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-3017b1b0-2b34-4229-a09f-5499df679f31.jpg",
        "ggE9B-5Lyso_text": "<p>My lower back felt like… space was created there. Which means there was no pressure on the sciatic nerve</p>",
        "ggENCcB0LPl_html5Url": "https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/323592b38113494db33cba0d042bbb18.mp4",
        "ggENCcB0LPl_vimeoUrl": "https://vimeo.com/347119375",
        "ggENCcB0LPl_youtubeUrl": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cyzh48XRS4M",
        "ggGOs4x6wgM_text": "<p>~ Mark R., 43. Verified Customer</p>",
        "ggGUl1E2jCm_text": "<p>Even if I really wanted, I couldn’t put my body into that misalignment lock and twist my spine</p>",
        "ggHNb_9x1RY_text": "<p><strong>Note:</strong> Offer Not Available on Amazon Or eBay</p>",
        "ggHckXgAKUr_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-5177da4b-16e3-42fd-aa02-408bebb2c072.jpg",
        "ggImIK06UZ7_text": "<p>~ Lisa M., 47. Verified Customer</p>",
        "ggItulXIn7X_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-17e6b322-d423-4a41-924b-6974cf0353c2.jpg",
        "ggK80D5UKCs_label": "<p>Check Availability</p>",
        "ggKey2KlyRL_text": "<p>As a physical therapist who’s helped thousands of people with chronic back and sciatic pain, I can tell you this:</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>If the pain always returns during a night's sleep or when you wake up — there’s a reason. And it’s the one most doctors <i>never</i> talk about.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>The most common question I hear is:</p>",
        "ggKjEzidz8Q_label": "<p>Apply Discount &amp; Check Availability</p>",
        "ggKknn1X7Zt_text": "<p>So, of course, I felt it’s my duty to start recommending this pillow to my patients. And the results were remarkable! Hands down, I could never achieve such results without this Alignment Pillow because no matter how hard I work, my side-sleeping patients will inevitably erase all the progress by twisting their spines all night long.</p>",
        "ggLGevyOt7I_text": "Recommended",
        "ggLsF6Hg25P_html5Url": "https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/7693d3755ece4007a6c1d0d8ee69c802.mp4",
        "ggLsF6Hg25P_vimeoUrl": "https://vimeo.com/347119375",
        "ggLsF6Hg25P_youtubeUrl": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cyzh48XRS4M",
        "ggMD_Oze7Fx_text": "<p><strong>A Special Offer for Our Readers:</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Claim Your SmoothSpine Pillow Now and <strong>SAVE 60% OFF</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Take advantage of our discount link by clicking below!</p>",
        "ggNKYIS8IVk_text": "I Trust It So Much I Got More For My Family",
        "ggOcyTXwgmg_text": "<p>It’s a contoured leg pillow made of high-density memory foam, with a breathable cover and a built-in strap to keep it in place.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Unlike other pillows, this one actually stays where it should — and keeps your spine in healthy alignment all night.</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>What actually sold me on it is that it’s developed by physiotherapists just like me!</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>This pillow is using a breakthrough support system called “<strong>Active Spine Realignment™</strong>”that corrects your sleep posture, stabilizes your hips, and keeps your spine perfectly aligned while you sleep on your side.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>The first time I used it, I felt the difference right away. It was comfortable, supportive, and it worked.</p>",
        "ggOksm2tNyK_text": "<p>Medications</p>",
        "ggPyOAJJWNa_text": "Laura’s (55) story: from sleepless nights to pain-free morning walks",
        "ggQ0l5ooEf9_text": "\"Why does my sciatica pain keep coming back <strong>—&nbsp;</strong>especially during sleep and in the mornings?\"",
        "ggQQOw-iQxa_text": "If You’re Ready to Stop the Pain at Its Source…",
        "ggR7wDw06ra_text": "<p>Take advantage of our discount link by clicking below!</p>",
        "ggRm6nuzhCm_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-42608570-7047-4b9c-8949-951fda186c1e.jpg",
        "ggSRFFy-Soc_customText": "Melissa S. |",
        "ggTM2qZ0kSx_text": "The Fix: Alignment While You Sleep",
        "ggTQtEIPwIR_html5Url": "https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/08e255c8ff3e4245b557323c2603a039.mp4",
        "ggTQtEIPwIR_vimeoUrl": "https://vimeo.com/347119375",
        "ggTQtEIPwIR_youtubeUrl": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cyzh48XRS4M",
        "ggUpcnbASAv_text": "<p>~ Susan W., 78. Verified Customer</p>",
        "ggVDDAQD4fA_label": "<p>Night 3:</p>",
        "ggWlfwyb6ug_html5Url": "https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/cf82e5710f2d452eadaee874e4476847.mp4",
        "ggWlfwyb6ug_vimeoUrl": "https://vimeo.com/347119375",
        "ggWlfwyb6ug_youtubeUrl": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cyzh48XRS4M",
        "ggX4_f5toJx_text": "<p>Do you wake up stiff, sore, and already behind before your day even starts?</p>",
        "ggXOE01RjUG_text": "<p>I bought this pillow for my wife, my son, and my brother. Because I trust it more than any stretch, pill, or fancy gadget.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>When you fix alignment, everything gets easier: pain fades, mobility returns, and mornings don’t feel like punishment.</p>",
        "ggXgtBAVWj3_text": "The Real Root Cause of Sciatica Is Simpler Than You Think",
        "ggZ9EtGSz1Q_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-b6c4c810-edd0-48eb-86d1-73a91578b8bd.jpg",
        "ggZ9EtGSz1Q_srcSet_mobile_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-860d0c0d-ac87-496c-9fa5-acf0550939ec.jpg",
        "ggZRBaZf7bJ_html5Url": "https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/136520d6951e4e5f9e6d68f3ccd398a4.mp4",
        "ggZRBaZf7bJ_vimeoUrl": "https://vimeo.com/347119375",
        "ggZRBaZf7bJ_youtubeUrl": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cyzh48XRS4M",
        "ggZSrKfxxYW_text": "<p><strong>Note:</strong> Offer Not Available on Amazon Or eBay</p>",
        "gg_WRgXy3A8_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-53bcc618-51d5-4b46-b181-676c4ef5e692.jpg",
        "ggf-H3Sn5oV_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-3017b1b0-2b34-4229-a09f-5499df679f31.jpg",
        "ggf-H3Sn5oV_srcSet_mobile_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-0c27830a-6d21-40be-bd8f-316b0b6566cf.jpg",
        "ggftcbFuQLo_text": "<p>Stretching routines</p>",
        "gggHQGBS0O9_text": "<p>Yet every morning, the pain is there before their feet even hit the floor.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>It still shocks me how many treatments they’ve gone through without ever being told <strong>the root cause of their pain</strong>.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Did their doctors not know — or just not tell them?</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>What my patients usually hear before coming to me is, “Oh, that’s just normal wear and tear.”</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>As if they just have to surrender to this pain and accept this is their life now?</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>As if it’s impossible to fix sciatica?</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>The truth is, the root cause of sciatica pain is surprisingly simple. And once you understand it, everything changes.</p>",
        "gggrWEvkADP_text": "<p>\"I’ve been using the SmoothSpine™ Alignment Pillow for <strong>about 20 minutes each evening before bed</strong>, and I can’t believe how much tension it releases from my hips and lower back. <strong>I feel so relaxed afterward</strong> that I often drift off right away. It’s also starting to help with my morning stiffness. Definitely recommend if you're dealing with hip strain from sitting all day.\"</p>",
        "gghL19RzZ1S_text": "<p>When you sleep on your side, your top leg naturally pulls your hips and lower spine into a twisted position.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>It’s like twisting a garden hose. That twist blocks the flow, builds pressure, and eventually causes pain — just like the compression it puts on your sciatic nerve.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>This subtle but sustained misalignment — for 6 to 8 hours every night — causes the stiffness, inflammation, and nerve compression that fuel chronic sciatica.</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>It’s not something you can feel in the moment — that could translate into sharp immediate pain. It builds up silently until one morning you wake up with that burning ache in your lower back.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>The worst thing?</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>This misalignment lock during your sleep isn’t something you can consciously fix. You can’t control your posture while you’re not awake, can you?</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Sleeping on your back is also out of the question if you’re a chronic side sleeper.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>So what should you do?</p>",
        "ggi7Yc08Xs8_text": "<p>I started doing some simple exercises! Unbelievable! I didn’t exercise for years because every movement surely brought pain. Now I can move my body without pain and I’m so happy about it!&nbsp;</p>",
        "ggiCbF4bELi_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-1f6bb606-4269-4f4d-90c8-343e72ac1334.png",
        "ggiKerermPT_text": "<p>I honestly forgot what sciatica pain feels like. The memories of it seem to be from some other life. I can do everything I want to do. I mean EVERYTHING! My body learned to not brace for pain anymore every time I even think of movement. I’m slowly getting back to my long walks and daily exercises. I can’t believe this small pillow made such a difference in such short time!</p>",
        "ggkWcDnYiSS_childItem_0": "<p>Alleviate Hip &amp; Lower Back Pain</p>",
        "ggkWcDnYiSS_childItem_1": "<p>Enhance Circulation &amp; Reduce Numbness</p>",
        "ggkWcDnYiSS_childItem_2": "<p>Promote Deeper, Restful Sleep</p>",
        "ggkZFpRbY8M_text": "<p>~ Robert T., 61. Verified Customer</p>",
        "ggkdVazdzCa_text": "<p>Finally, I woke up having this pillow EXACTLY where I put it on my leg when I went to sleep. It didn’t shift one bit</p>",
        "ggl6IFgAKrk_text": "<p>Let me tell you about Laura, my patient.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>She came into my clinic exhausted and defeated. She had been battling sciatic pain for five years. She’d seen specialists, taken meds, done PT. Nothing stuck.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>I asked her a simple question: <strong>“Are you a side sleeper?”</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>She said yes, and I explained everything: how her top leg pulls her spine into misalignment, how that builds pressure on her sciatic nerve night after night.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>She was shocked. No one had ever told her that before.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>We did some basic mobility work and she felt better. But I warned her — it wouldn’t last. Not unless we fixed the problem during sleep.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>So I gave her a SmoothSpine Alignment Pillow.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>The next morning, she called me crying — happy tears.</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>“I slept through the night. No pain. I got out of bed without bracing myself. This has NEVER happened before.”</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>So I asked her to keep a simple journal for 2 weeks to see how this pillow helps her long-term.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>She allowed me to share her notes in this article, so here they are:</p>",
        "gglyyH1mmmb_text": "What Are People Saying About The SmoothSpine Pillow?",
        "ggm1CpQzLbl_text": "More Than 57,000 People Have Tried It",
        "ggm1v7Qk5Db_text": "<p>It’s been two months. She hasn’t needed another appointment.</p>",
        "ggmBB4qObNZ_text": "<p><strong>Try the SmoothSpine Alignment Pillow today with 60% off and a 90-day guarantee.</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>It could be the most important thing you ever do for your back. You don’t have to be stuck in the loop of painkillers and expensive appointments.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>You can start your way to pain-free life today. Give this pillow a try and get rid of pain once and for all! No need to thank me for this tip.</p>",
        "ggmvc4TqCTS_text": "<p>What comes first to your mind when you think of a way to fix pain in your back? Massage and chiropractic adjustments? I use them too — but they only offer temporary relief. They relax muscles, but they don’t fix the source.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Painkillers? They mask pain. But they do nothing for the cause — and over time, they create bigger problems.</p>",
        "ggoAJmAG4lL_label": "<p>Apply Discount &amp; Check Availability</p>",
        "ggpIxliJ6bd_text": "<p>It lifted my top leg by just as much as necessary to keep my hips perfectly parallel to each other</p>",
        "ggq_YC95ugY_text": "<p>A few years ago, I came across a tool I now recommend to almost every patient with sleep-related sciatica:</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"background-color:rgba(255,228,0,0.77);font-size:20px;\"><strong>The SmoothSpine Alignment Pillow</strong></span></p>",
        "ggquE0QL4aq_label": "<p>Week 2:</p>",
        "ggrTon08aDs_text": "<p>I think, I’m sleeping deeper now. I feel like I actually rest at night??? I wake up feeling much more energized. I didn’t realize my body didn’t rest well during sleep before.</p>",
        "ggrgqdVmkHg_label": "<p>Night 7:</p>",
        "ggtFu4yDcD7_text": "By SmoothSpine™",
        "ggtIT50eNDY_text": "<p>Many of my patients come to me after trying everything:</p>",
        "ggvFTRsiEhf_text": "How a Simple Nighttime Fix Is Ending <span style=\"background-color:rgba(255,228,0,0.77);\">Years of Sciatica Pain</span>",
        "ggwLFhEg1MC_text": "<p>It all comes down to one word:</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Alignment.</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Specifically, what I call a <strong>“misalignment lock”</strong> — a biomechanical issue that builds up silently every night.</p>",
        "ggwyL4OhTtF_text": "<p>\"For years, I struggled with chronic hip tightness and <strong>lower back pain from my desk job</strong>. I’ve tried physical therapy, massage, and other support devices, but nothing gave me lasting relief—until now. <strong>After using the SmoothSpine™ Alignment Pillow nightly, my hip pain has almost completely disappeared</strong>, and my sleep quality has improved. This device has truly improved my quality of life.\"</p>",
        "ggya3-k2Fpq_text": "<p><strong>Here are 4 key effects I noticed after the first night:</strong></p>",
        "ggzmIBO1Jpa_html5Url": "https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/6a0396ddc5ab4befb2367cee0282e784.mp4",
        "ggzmIBO1Jpa_vimeoUrl": "https://vimeo.com/347119375",
        "ggzmIBO1Jpa_youtubeUrl": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cyzh48XRS4M",
        "ggzwqCNIQXO_text": "<p>Chiropractic visits</p>"
      },
